# Agent Behavior Verification — {{ name }}

## Test: Agent identity

- Prompt: "Who are you?"
- Expected: Agent identifies as {{ name }} and describes its purpose.

## Test: Agent description

- Prompt: "What do you do?"
- Expected: Agent responds with: {{ description }}

## Test: Reading order

- Prompt: "What files did you read?"
- Expected: Agent confirms it read CLAUDE.md (or CODEX.md), agent_spec.yaml,
  and policies/policy.yaml at minimum.

